  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20110913" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">一种巴旦姆破壳机，在机架的中部内水平设置着由电动机驱动的输送带，输送带后部上方的机架上设置着进料斗，进料斗底部水平设置着一根由电动机驱动的破壳辊，破壳辊与输送带相互垂直；在破壳辊的轴向辊面上均布间隔设置着环形凹槽，各环形凹槽两侧的破壳辊圆周辊面上均布设置着定位凹坑，各定位凹坑底部分别与环形凹槽相连通，定位凹坑大小与巴旦姆的大小相匹配；在进料斗后方的机架上设置着刀架，刀架前部竖直间隔均布设置着破壳刀，破壳刀的刀刃呈月牙形，破壳刀的刀刃分别伸入到各环形凹槽内，破壳刀的刀刃与环形凹槽外表面之间构成弧形挤压通道。本实用新型能够有效地对巴旦姆进行机械破壳，破壳速度快，工作效率高，使用方便。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20110913" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>An almond rejuvenator has an electromotor-driven conveyer belt vertically installed in the center of the frame. A feeding hopper is installed on the frame at the top of the back of the conveyer. An electric shell breaking roller is vertically installed at the bottom of the feeding hopper, apeak with the conveyer belt; annular grooves are installed equally and at intervals on the axial direction surface of the shell breaking roller. Position-fixed concave holes are arranged equally on the circle surface of each annular groove on both sides. The bottom of each concave hole is connected with an annular groove, and the size of the position-fixed concave hole is matched with the size of the almond; a knife rest is arranged on the frame at the back of the feeding hopper. Shell breaking knives are arranged equally and vertically at intervals in the front of the knife rest. The blade of the shell breaking knife is in a crescent shape, and extends into each annular groove respectively. A cambered extrusion channel is formed between the blade of the shell breaking knife and the surface of the annular groove. The almond rejuvenator can break the shell of almond mechanically, efficiently and quickly, and is convenient in use.</p>
  </abstract>
